---
title: Extra Cheesy Capsicum Hasselback Chicken with Potato Wedges & Cucumber Salad
description: Get ready for a bite of cheesy perfection! Juicy, golden chicken topped with smokey capsicum relish and ooey gooey melted cheese. Nestled alongside crisp potato wedges and a crunchy cucumber salad, this one-pan wonder is packed with bold flavours and minimal fuss.
